Package: coursedown
Title: Creating course matetials using RMarkdown
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Abhijit",
           family = "Dasgupta",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "aikidasgupta@gmail.com")
Description: 
  This package sets up a directory structure  and template files to run a R-based course. This includes
  creating slides for lectures in `xaringan` format, a course notes website using bookdown, potentially based
  on the slides, and a class website using RMarkdown.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
